9/poem-LITAao_4q8_sZITFcSHOcA">Tống An Nam Bùi đô hộ - 送安南裴都護</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Quy%E1%BB%81n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-D%C6%B0/author-_4d5nEBX-lxP-MgaFitnXg">Quyền Đức Dư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu%C3%A2n-B%C3%A1/T%E1%BB%91ng-k%E1%BB%B9-nh%C3%A2n-xu%E1%BA%A5t-gia/poem-0gqNqchx22cgA__cO8P4Rg">Tống kỹ nhân xuất gia - 送妓人出家</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu%C3%A2n-B%C3%A1/author-S5rZQ2X8fGxN2NHpm8VG9A">Dương Tuân Bá</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-Th%C3%A0nh-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Tri%E1%BB%81u-Ti%C3%AAn-qu%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%91%E1%BA%A3o/poem-k1azVfdswKnBXLw7JxxXsg">Triều Tiên quần đảo - 朝鮮群島</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1c-Th%C3%A0nh-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-Jg_4_inbL47zGqzn3fJTrw">Lạc Thành Tương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-%C3%82n/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-An-th%C3%A2n-c%E1%BB%91/poem-Ynu9lITGyvlz6AoDfCix4g">Trường An thân cố - 長安親故</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-%C3%82n/author-p2FSS_aHoApfOIrlh-6pOg">Lư Ân</a>)<br></div>	</div>
